<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="1" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},&nbsp;<br><br>Thank you for contacting Kingsbridge. Following our conversation, please find attached some information about our&nbsp;<b>Cyber Liability Cover</b>.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br><br>This policy offers up to £100,000 in protection against a cyber attack on your business.<br><br>Our product has been tailored to cover the main risks you face as a contractor.&nbsp;<br><br>The key features of this package are:&nbsp;</font></p><p class="MsoNormal"></p><ul><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">24/7 cyber incident helpline (no excess for any expert guidance or initial advice)</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Up to £25,000 cyber extortion and ransom costs&nbsp;</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Up to £100,000 regulatory defense and penalties&nbsp;</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Up to £100,000 system and data rectification costs&nbsp;</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Up to £20,000 business interruption costs&nbsp;</font></li></ul><p></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">The standard package price, subject to eligibility, is £100 plus Insurance Premium Tax at 12% for the year. Find out&nbsp;<a href="https://www.kingsbridge.co.uk/products/cyber-liability-insurance">more information via our website</a>.<br><br>If you have any questions or wish to discuss this product in more detail, please give me a call on&nbsp;<b>01242 808 740</b>.<br><br>Kind regards<span style="background-color: white;">,<br></span><span style="background-color: white;"><br>{!User.FirstName}&nbsp;<br></span><span style="background-color: white;">Sales Team<br></span><span style="background-color: white;"><br>E: salesteam@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><font style="background-color: white;">T:&nbsp;</font><font style="background-color: white;">01242 808740</font></font></p>]]></td>
</tr>
